Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.77,0:00:02.80,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,看 好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.71,0:00:08.34,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,多练练你也能做到这样子哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.19,0:00:10.40,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你 重叔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.93,0:00:19.09,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了你 就像是得了个孙女一样
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.44,0:00:21.64,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这不过是一时兴起嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.85,0:00:27.33,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这样弄… 成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.47,0:00:32.19,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,坏了 不知不觉就入迷了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.79,0:00:34.97,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,蜡烛也给我浪费掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.81,0:00:37.44,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,还是睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.06,0:00:40.83,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,看 厉害吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.41,0:00:44.14,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我教你 我们一起玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.47,0:00:47.17,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,还是游戏有意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.15,0:00:49.96,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,什么嘛 那就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.02,0:00:50.84,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.92,0:00:52.11,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,大笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.83,0:00:58.05,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,说人笨蛋的人才是笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.79,0:01:02.87,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就算你说玩游戏… 人家买不起嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.50,0:01:07.63,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,钱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.32,0:01:09.16,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,钱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.98,0:01:10.96,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,钱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.44,0:01:13.39,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,钱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.13,0:01:20.62,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,钱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.09,0:01:24.64,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,要是我再有钱一点的话
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.77,0:01:26.22,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,应该就能买游戏了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.64,0:01:29.13,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我该怎么做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.22,0:01:35.06,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,原来走一天赚到的钱 就让我很满足了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.81,0:01:40.62,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,可一有时间了我就想玩 想要钱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.96,0:01:45.02,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,人一旦有了余裕 就不满足于现状了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.93,0:01:50.05,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,人类究竟是有多贪婪啊
