Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.12,0:02:26.48,hinamatsuri_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}思い出の中　微笑んでるその横顔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.75,0:02:32.16,hinamatsuri_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}何気ない日々が　大切なんだと
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.42,0:02:37.01,hinamatsuri_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}思う気持ち　それに今気付いたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.17,0:02:39.82,hinamatsuri_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}君と笑って過ごした日
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.82,0:02:42.63,hinamatsuri_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}君と言い合って泣いた日
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.65,0:02:46.99,hinamatsuri_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}君と過ごした日々　愛しい日々
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.27,0:02:49.76,hinamatsuri_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}大切だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.49,0:02:55.19,hinamatsuri_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}ねえ　どれだけ離れているのかな
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.54,0:03:01.44,hinamatsuri_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}君の温もり思い出しているよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.52,0:03:06.25,hinamatsuri_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}遠くに見えるあの街の灯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.34,0:03:10.74,hinamatsuri_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}君は笑えてるかな
Comment: 0,0:01:22.00,0:01:22.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.83,0:01:58.30,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}我们究竟相距多远呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.40,0:02:05.40,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}偶然一瞬 想起了你的容貌模样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.12,0:02:26.48,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}在记忆之中 你微笑着的侧脸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.75,0:02:32.16,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}平淡无奇的日常 是无可替的宝物
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.24,0:02:37.01,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}这份思念之情 现在终于意识到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.17,0:02:39.82,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}和你欢笑度过的时光
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.82,0:02:42.63,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}和你争论泪流的曾经
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.65,0:02:46.99,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}我们携手的每一天 令人无比怜爱的每一天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.27,0:02:49.76,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}十分珍惜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.49,0:02:55.19,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}我们究竟相距多远呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.54,0:03:01.44,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}我又回忆起你的温暖
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.52,0:03:06.25,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}遥遥可见的那条街道的灯火
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.34,0:03:10.74,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}你正展露着笑容吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,——OP——
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.62,0:03:25.35,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,快看啊 雏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.97,0:03:25.47,hinamatsuri_paper,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs60\c&H968E8B&\pos(408,714)}电视\N空调 \N电风扇\N音响\N游戏机\N同上\N{\fs55}数码相机\N电动车
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.97,0:03:25.47,hinamatsuri_paper,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs60\pos(1520,736)}打印机 \N冰箱\N 微波炉\N 吸尘器\N 缝纫机 \N洗衣机 \N取暖器\N 电饭锅
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.18,0:03:27.19,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.51,0:03:32.85,hinamatsuri_guochang,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fad(960,834)}第五话 三个臭皮匠赛过诸葛亮
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.68,0:03:29.26,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我从泰叔那里打听到的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.54,0:03:33.01,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我听说有个叫吉田的流浪汉在回收旧家电
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.50,0:03:37.21,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你看 一台电视可是能卖3000元啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.92,0:03:40.66,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,所以啊雏 咱们出发吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.30,0:03:43.80,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,该去哪里找呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.40,0:03:46.30,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,大概是没什么人来的地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.02,0:03:51.72,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我之前还看到过类似呢 真是可惜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.89,0:03:54.26,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,杏子 是那个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.54,0:04:00.30,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,突然间就找到电视了 而且还有这么多
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.85,0:04:03.75,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,太棒了 真是一座宝山啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.82,0:04:06.33,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你先在这里守一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.36,0:04:09.06,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好累啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.95,0:04:11.59,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,快到了 加把劲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.84,0:04:12.73,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.13,0:04:15.73,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不过还真是重啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.79,0:04:18.42,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,吉田
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.73,0:04:20.61,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.14,0:04:23.29,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真没想到一天的工夫 你就找到了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.00,0:04:25.76,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,一个流浪汉居然过得这么有品位
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.97,0:04:27.60,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,「居然」？ 你谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.16,0:04:31.58,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我的宝山啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.70,0:04:36.32,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不 这些是垃圾
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.34,0:04:39.89,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真亏你能找这么多
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.95,0:04:41.71,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么啊 这不是电视吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.72,0:04:43.82,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,现在显像管这东西不值钱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.29,0:04:46.96,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不过因为能卖给东南亚 所以我就收了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.17,0:04:48.02,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那你给多少
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.04,0:04:50.81,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,10元
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.04,0:04:52.09,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么这样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.47,0:04:55.37,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,只有数字信号的液晶电视才能买三千元啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.75,0:04:57.46,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,找这种电视可不太容易啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.63,0:05:01.05,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,一个流浪的搞回收干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.26,0:05:02.31,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你想跟我吵架吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.01,0:05:03.71,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,雏
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.95,0:05:07.58,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,他点燃了我的斗志…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.15,0:05:10.78,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,要是这样的话 我偏要找一台
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.66,0:05:14.70,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,找不到啊 两个人的话这已经是极限了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.17,0:05:16.54,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我要累死了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.64,0:05:17.70,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但 但是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.83,0:05:22.70,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,雏？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.88,0:05:25.73,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我找人来帮我们了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.64,0:05:30.57,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我也把瞳给叫来帮忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.10,0:05:33.09,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我 我的朋友 瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.54,0:05:37.34,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,话说我根本联系不到她啊 就算她是我的朋友…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.47,0:05:38.37,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,小雏
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.48,0:05:41.24,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.02,0:05:42.97,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,杏子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.24,0:05:46.14,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你为什么会… 你和雏认识吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.06,0:05:49.44,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,她是我学校里的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.29,0:05:54.55,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊 你跟雏早就是朋友了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.62,0:06:02.86,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 天马上就要黑了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.03,0:06:04.84,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,今天估计找不到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.55,0:06:09.54,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但好不容易才找到你们两个来帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.75,0:06:10.91,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,找不到实在是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.87,0:06:18.07,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那我就去那边找 咱们再加把劲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.10,0:06:26.90,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 妈 咱们之前不是买了台新电视吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.53,0:06:30.89,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,之前还想把旧的给扔了来着
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.17,0:06:43.29,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈其实不用特地把它装箱子里的啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.38,0:06:45.59,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就放这边吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.95,0:06:50.88,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 这样杏子就…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.93,0:06:51.67,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我说你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.07,0:06:55.04,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.79,0:06:58.16,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你还要找吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.33,0:07:00.06,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在连一台都没找到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.53,0:07:05.92,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,现在瞳肯定也在努力找啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.27,0:07:09.39,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你啊 可不能乱大件垃圾啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.53,0:07:13.62,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你一直不说话 是说不出口吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.25,0:07:17.39,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是说了真话 他似乎也不会相信啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.51,0:07:21.00,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就算他信了 问题依然不小啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.14,0:07:22.01,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那没办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.73,0:07:24.39,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,总之先跟你的家人联系一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.60,0:07:28.60,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 千万不要… 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.74,0:07:32.23,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我并不是想责怪你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.81,0:07:34.13,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我从开始就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.23,0:07:36.94,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你实话跟我说就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.56,0:07:41.52,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你是被家长逼着出来扔东西的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.94,0:07:44.06,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,根本不是这么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.84,0:07:46.18,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这样下去不行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.80,0:07:49.33,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,咱们得学学瞳 分头去找电视吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.16,0:07:54.41,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这儿多的是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.51,0:07:56.62,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你想买电视
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.60,0:07:59.18,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,客厅不是有一台吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.44,0:08:00.56,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我想再另买一台
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.66,0:08:06.36,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这些应该够买一台了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.03,0:08:09.49,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下 就这么轻易答应真的好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.66,0:08:11.83,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的 好不容易喝得挺开心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.84,0:08:13.42,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就别在这儿开家庭会议了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.46,0:08:16.37,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,反正都要买 那就在「惊吓相机」那里买吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.66,0:08:17.66,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,积分卡吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.70,0:08:22.44,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,要去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.69,0:08:23.48,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,去河边
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.67,0:08:24.30,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,哪里的？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.48,0:08:27.63,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我把电视给带来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.81,0:08:31.42,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不不不… 这怎么看都是全新的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.00,0:08:33.40,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要卖这个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.85,0:08:35.58,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,她是在试探我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.41,0:08:39.57,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 完全不知道她在想什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.28,0:08:41.08,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 小姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.44,0:08:45.63,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,车费一共是5920元 你会付钱给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.96,0:08:46.75,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我没钱哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.33,0:08:49.57,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那我帮她付吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.22,0:08:52.06,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就当是我收这台电视的钱可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.31,0:08:54.59,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你能付的话倒是也行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.22,0:08:57.91,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但这台电视是她刚刚在「惊吓相机」买的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.34,0:08:59.27,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,她到底想干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.58,0:09:00.73,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这事别问我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.93,0:09:04.51,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,雏
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.01,0:09:09.53,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我没找到电视
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.79,0:09:11.10,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我也失败了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.45,0:09:12.31,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.56,0:09:14.48,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,看来今天是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.97,0:09:20.12,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,瞳 这是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.20,0:09:22.26,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.07,0:09:24.78,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然在半路上没能扔掉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.90,0:09:26.12,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,太棒了 太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.43,0:09:29.18,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,哎 你好像不太高兴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.35,0:09:30.87,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不 哪有这回事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.08,0:09:33.44,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好开心 好开心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.85,0:09:37.59,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真不愧是瞳啊 区区一台电视不用太高兴对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.96,0:09:39.00,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.39,0:09:41.80,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,又装在箱子里…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.93,0:09:43.32,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对不是垃圾
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.91,0:09:47.19,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然这话也不该我来说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.90,0:09:49.94,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你们干脆卖到回收店去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.79,0:09:54.79,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到今天赚到了这么多钱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.31,0:09:58.35,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 这是瞳找到的 我收下真的好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.53,0:10:02.56,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我就算是找到了 要是没听你说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.87,0:10:04.75,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不会拿它来换钱的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.88,0:10:07.52,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那咱们三个人平分了吧 这样好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.17,0:10:09.35,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.49,0:10:12.90,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你为什么突然间就想要钱了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.98,0:10:16.48,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,因 因为
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.42,0:10:21.73,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你说游戏很有趣 我想跟你一起玩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.40,0:10:24.42,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.43,0:10:25.38,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你已经全说了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.50,0:10:27.50,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.91,0:10:29.48,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,买到电视了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.41,0:10:32.99,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗 可能过个几天就会送来了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.88,0:10:34.98,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我把电视给卖了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.98,0:10:35.78,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.67,0:10:37.50,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那卖的钱…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.69,0:10:39.22,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不对 我想问的不是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.44,0:10:41.02,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我付车钱用完了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.58,0:10:44.17,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么会这样 猜谜游戏吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.95,0:10:46.98,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下啊 健吾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.00,0:10:49.54,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,再不快点回去的话老妈会发火的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.50,0:10:52.19,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,欸那不是三岛吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.62,0:10:55.65,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真的耶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.15,0:11:05.24,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,诶 Little Song酒吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.03,0:11:07.44,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么在这种地方
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.64,0:11:09.60,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 贵志
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.37,0:11:11.53,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那是松谷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.91,0:11:12.91,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.28,0:11:19.88,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂 他进去那里了诶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.49,0:11:22.54,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,老师跟学生在酒吧里见面
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.81,0:11:27.15,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,难道是不纯异性交往？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.18,0:11:28.34,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是挺好的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.35,0:11:30.46,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊咧 不要
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.10,0:11:32.37,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,然后呢 然后呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.41,0:11:33.48,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,会揉胸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.50,0:11:34.33,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,会揉啊？！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.83,0:11:37.65,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 接下来的妄想进行不下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.66,0:11:39.76,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,知识 如果再有多一点知识的话！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.82,0:11:43.99,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 那个该死萝莉控老师
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.99,0:11:45.50,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,必须制裁他啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.72,0:11:48.47,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,0)\an8}怀疑松谷进行不纯异性交往对策本部
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.89,0:11:51.42,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,诸位 对为了解决事件而聚集起来的你们表示感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.53,0:11:54.86,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不 就只有我而已
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.16,0:11:56.88,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我们不想让太多人知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.52,0:11:59.52,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,因为还关系到她的名誉嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.44,0:12:02.42,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,瞳才不会做那种事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.69,0:12:03.79,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,反正是你们看错了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.03,0:12:07.95,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,瞧您说的 相泽警视
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.08,0:12:10.51,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就像在说上头的人是看不见现场发生的事似的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.27,0:12:13.53,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,如果要玩警察游戏的话就把雏也喊上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.79,0:12:14.91,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就算那家伙来了也没用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.92,0:12:16.20,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,别这么说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.83,0:12:19.29,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然完全没用处 但是吉祥物还是能当的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.30,0:12:20.48,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你才是别那么说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.37,0:12:22.84,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真是没办法 健吾巡查部长
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.09,0:12:24.37,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,去把雏巡查喊过来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.42,0:12:25.93,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,了解 贵志警部
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.42,0:12:25.93,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}注：警视，警部，巡查部长，巡查都是警察官的职位，阶级依次递减
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.94,0:12:27.46,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这两人只是在玩而已吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.53,0:12:32.57,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,警部 我把雏巡查带过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.60,0:12:33.44,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你们在干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.04,0:12:34.99,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,雏巡查
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.88,0:12:37.67,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我对你不报任何期待
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.70,0:12:39.10,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,叫她过来就这个语气？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.84,0:12:41.17,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 接下来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.38,0:12:45.27,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,能请你先交给我来办吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.63,0:12:46.86,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,警视亲自来？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.46,0:12:49.02,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我是她的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.16,0:12:51.46,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,跟你们不同
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.84,0:12:54.78,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我是为了澄清她的嫌疑才进行的行动
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.80,0:12:55.95,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,噢噢噢 相泽警视
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.95,0:12:56.98,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是干劲十足嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.09,0:12:58.26,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 这是在干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.30,0:13:02.55,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,话虽这么说 姑且先刺探一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.60,0:13:04.97,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来啊瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.78,0:13:08.31,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,有人在晚上的繁华街那边看到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.18,0:13:12.39,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不 那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.99,0:13:15.81,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,补习班 我是去补习班啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.67,0:13:21.53,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那一带的话是开心塾吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.69,0:13:22.99,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.29,0:13:25.39,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,有个叫吉田的讲师很有名
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.49,0:13:26.45,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,瞳你是在跟他学吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.78,0:13:30.53,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊不 吉田老师没教我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.74,0:13:31.81,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,因为很受欢迎嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.03,0:13:33.35,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊记错了是吉野
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.42,0:13:35.74,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊不对 是吉野老师呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.73,0:13:38.54,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我稍微去一下厕所
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.59,0:13:43.28,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,还说「哎呀」 你是中国人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.76,0:13:46.82,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的话反而想让她说一下「阿鲁」之类词尾呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.76,0:13:46.82,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}注：这里捏他神乐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.91,0:13:49.70,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不不不冷静一下相泽纱夜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.05,0:13:51.28,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,别丢了原本目的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.27,0:13:53.47,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.18,0:13:57.01,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不过并没有那个讲师呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.46,0:14:01.11,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊嗯 我是知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.16,0:14:03.42,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,只是说不出口是纱夜你搞错了而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.53,0:14:06.43,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 真是头疼 哎呀…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.54,0:14:09.42,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 虽然我是不信啦但这个态度…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.06,0:14:12.61,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛应该是被卷进什么麻烦事了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.98,0:14:14.94,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来啊瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.94,0:14:17.34,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道Little Song吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.73,0:14:19.53,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊好脏
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.61,0:14:21.08,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,三岛把牛奶喷出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.19,0:14:22.87,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,别闹了啊 我都黏乎乎的了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.95,0:14:25.07,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不 如果是三岛的牛奶的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.62,0:14:26.39,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.54,0:14:27.78,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不 完全不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.98,0:14:33.83,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.04,0:14:36.98,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,总觉得变得好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.65,0:14:40.35,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我说的是瞳你喜欢的「中央公园」的曲子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.40,0:14:41.71,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 出了这样的歌吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.47,0:14:44.21,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不 完全是我瞎编的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.22,0:14:45.05,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,到底想怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.83,0:14:48.45,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这样 她没说漏嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.58,0:14:51.42,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,喂　你有真的有打算让犯人落网吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.43,0:14:52.99,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你只是在跟三岛玩而已吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.42,0:14:55.39,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,相泽警视
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.40,0:14:56.56,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你说点什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.30,0:15:01.88,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,慌慌张张的瞳 总而言之就是很可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.90,0:15:03.34,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那你这不就是在玩而已嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.40,0:15:04.92,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}散伙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.60,0:15:06.13,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 你们在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.97,0:15:06.53,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}我们自己来搞定
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.34,0:15:08.40,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 还真敢说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.38,0:15:15.33,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 这个时候要分开走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.45,0:15:17.82,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,楼梯只有这个 没办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.71,0:15:20.46,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,搞什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.11,0:15:22.81,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来怎么办 警部
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.05,0:15:24.91,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我们两个去收集证据吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.02,0:15:28.34,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,如果他们有猫腻 可能在学校里也会独处
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.66,0:15:34.19,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,在 在学校 太糟了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.20,0:15:36.32,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,别这样啊 感觉都紧张起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.23,0:15:41.72,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,三岛 能稍微到准备室来一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.06,0:15:42.79,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.89,0:15:45.26,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,也太快了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.70,0:15:52.56,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.90,0:15:58.87,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,准备室
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.22,0:16:00.88,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,在这里面他们孤男寡女的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.95,0:16:03.66,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,孤男寡女地做什么呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.97,0:16:06.15,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊咧 不要
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.33,0:16:08.03,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,只能想象到这里！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.55,0:16:10.36,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,没办法了 进去捉个现成吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.39,0:16:12.43,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 就算真的看到了些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.44,0:16:14.00,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,为了搜查也是不得已的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.03,0:16:14.64,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.07,0:16:15.74,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,突入
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.94,0:16:17.24,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.55,0:16:20.11,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你们两个干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.73,0:16:23.58,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 讲义掉到四处都是了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.11,0:16:26.52,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你们两个 给三岛搭把手搬回去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.08,0:16:34.31,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我说三岛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.81,0:16:35.78,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.38,0:16:39.24,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你是不是在做什么不能告诉别人的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.70,0:16:44.53,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,什 什 你指什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.89,0:16:47.19,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这是多么显而易见的可疑态度啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.45,0:16:48.22,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.46,0:16:49.82,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你在做什么蠢事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.23,0:16:51.43,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,居然说是蠢事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.71,0:16:55.28,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那虽然是不能对人说 不过有人会感到高兴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.68,0:16:56.58,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,乐意？！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.85,0:16:59.85,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 当然我不知道你说的是什么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.18,0:17:03.95,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,健吾
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.20,0:17:06.26,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,讲义…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.08,0:17:08.08,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,松谷
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.22,0:17:11.06,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定要逮住你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.16,0:17:12.61,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,逮住你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.69,0:17:14.57,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对要把你抓个现成！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.72,0:17:20.22,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,别说是拿过去了 这都散成一地回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.22,0:17:23.54,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,然后呢 知道了些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.12,0:17:28.07,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,相泽 你也来帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.67,0:17:32.67,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我们 绝对要解决事件
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.80,0:17:36.80,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,必须对那个该死的邪门歪道的老师降下正义铁锤
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.59,0:17:40.10,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这两人情绪好高啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.30,0:17:42.45,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,来了 是三岛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.79,0:17:48.96,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs110\fn@思源黑体 CN Regular\frz269.8\c&H81B196&\3c&HD4FFE5&\b1\pos(632,488)}大人的玩具 干个痛快
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.86,0:17:46.67,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,进去了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.40,0:17:48.43,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,原来是真的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.16,0:17:50.33,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好 接下来就等…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.34,0:17:51.15,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这是在干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.59,0:17:54.75,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,松谷还没来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.83,0:17:55.84,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 现在在干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.38,0:17:58.33,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不不难道说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.35,0:17:59.16,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.59,0:18:01.70,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不 这不只是松谷
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.22,0:18:04.00,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是所谓的「援交」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.74,0:18:08.30,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,瞳 瞳才不会那种事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.31,0:18:09.76,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,看到犯罪现场后就慌了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.77,0:18:11.59,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,她可是说了「有人会感到高兴」啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.35,0:18:14.77,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是新田
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.98,0:18:19.47,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,新田是雏你老爸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.70,0:18:20.21,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.66,0:18:22.94,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,等 等等…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.53,0:18:25.64,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,雏的老爸进去啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.96,0:18:27.59,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真的假的 真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.71,0:18:30.86,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是说雏的老爸在跟三岛交往吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.12,0:18:35.07,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,看啊雏 那边有你的新妈妈哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.31,0:18:36.67,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你也晕头了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.79,0:18:38.28,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那边是酒吧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.30,0:18:40.27,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,也有从那里展开的故事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.28,0:18:41.53,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我怎么会容许它展开！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.23,0:18:43.65,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,如果那种事发生了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.04,0:18:46.61,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不就完全出局了吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.76,0:18:47.39,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,相泽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.31,0:18:51.16,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,瞳 瞳 瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.86,0:18:52.60,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.63,0:18:55.33,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎光…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.37,0:19:09.27,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,相泽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.57,0:19:11.51,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这个情况 是安全了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.87,0:19:13.38,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.11,0:19:20.09,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然搞不清楚情况  但这不是援交
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.60,0:19:23.68,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就是啊 不是最糟的情况
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.08,0:19:26.42,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 我们在担心你哦三岛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.43,0:19:27.75,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么在做调酒师啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.96,0:19:29.93,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你们
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.43,0:19:34.04,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,酒吧可不是小孩子能来的地方哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.47,0:19:38.84,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙是打算装作不认识我们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.97,0:19:41.46,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,被我们看到这副模样后她还以为还能蒙混过关吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.80,0:19:43.19,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,瞳 没你这样的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.20,0:19:45.17,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,警视 犯人在否认罪行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.30,0:19:46.26,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这里就交给我们
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.79,0:19:47.94,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 给我坦白
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.06,0:19:49.62,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你小子老家在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.00,0:19:53.51,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,请别在 店里进行审判…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.52,0:19:54.79,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.63,0:19:55.82,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}那 那个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.83,0:19:56.42,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 要糟啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.97,0:19:57.93,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.31,0:20:03.05,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我们几个 是担心你有个万一
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.83,0:20:06.75,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,如果瞳你不想说的话就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.87,0:20:09.64,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 至少告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.58,0:20:11.88,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,瞳你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.07,0:20:14.48,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我是真的在担心你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.01,0:20:19.83,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我们 是朋友嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.89,0:20:28.29,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起纱夜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.64,0:20:30.14,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我没事哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.79,0:20:32.73,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,诶 这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.20,0:20:37.41,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你为什么知道我叫纱夜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.18,0:20:45.59,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,放弃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.67,0:20:47.99,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,别再让老家的妈妈再哭泣了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.64,0:20:52.52,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,瞒着大家 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.95,0:20:55.20,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那老实地招供吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.92,0:20:59.14,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,说「我明明是个中学生 却在做着调酒师」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.54,0:21:05.05,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我明明是个中学生 却在做着调酒师
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.96,0:21:07.62,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,复述
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.64,0:21:10.55,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我明明是个中学生 却在做着调酒师
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.56,0:21:11.68,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,声音再大一点!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.71,0:21:15.83,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我明明是个中学生 却在做着调酒师
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.02,0:21:17.20,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,再大声一点！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.21,0:21:20.28,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我明明是个中学生 却在做着调酒师
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.29,0:21:23.16,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,再融入些心意 用偶像自我介绍风格说！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.94,0:21:29.09,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我明明是个中学生 却在做着调酒师
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.70,0:21:38.34,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.60,0:21:40.41,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.66,0:21:42.67,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 这是在干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.84,0:21:48.14,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 你们 为什么在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.23,0:21:49.53,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,松谷老师
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.60,0:21:52.85,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.85,0:21:55.73,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,跟三岛搞混了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.18,0:21:58.42,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,瞳真的跟三岛很像呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.41,0:22:02.44,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,出现了个高级的笨蛋啊
